reference:
  XML-RPC Functions
  XML-RPC




    &reftitle.intro;


     These functions can be used to write XML-RPC servers and clients.
     You can find more information about XML-RPC at
     &url.xmlrpc;, and more
     documentation on this extension and its functions at
     &url.xmlrpc-epi;.

